		<td class=subject><div class="subject">■ 電話がつながると落ちる現象</div></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td bgcolor="#ffffff">
			<table width="100%" border=0 cellpadding=1 cellspacing=0>
			<tr><td width="1%" nowrap valign=top>投稿者：</td><td width="99%" colspan=2><b>初心者</b> さん　　<span style="font-size:80%;">( uid 17149, posts:1, since 2003/05/22 )</span>
